Articles.Content: I have about 6 mods istalled and they are all updated to latest version but i cant seem to finish building the hum to my space 7-11 without the game crashing (aka my game crashes 2 min into gameplay) and ksp is my most relaxing game and im gonna self combust if this doesnt get fixed soon plz help!!!

I'm having the same issue, and I think it has something to do with my video card. I still haven't managed to pin down the exact root of the issue, or anything to remedy it though. I also experience frequent BSODs, and frequent crashing happens with Vivecraft and Job Simulator too. The card is an AMD Radeon R9 200 / HD 7900 Series, updated to the latest drivers.
